author: Home Repair Tutor
description: Pipe insulation tips…air leaks through pipes are problematic in old homes. I use Great Stuff Gaps and Cracks Pro to fill those voids. I love using the spray foam gun because I can adjust the size of the foam. When possible I seal both sides of the pipe to reduce air leaks and hopefully utility bills.
